                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9358" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-1060</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">895 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字向善：享道出行的负责任创新实践</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Digital for Good: Responsible innovation practices of XiangDao Travel</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张毛龙，卞元超，丛一丹，乔竹君，徐嘉鸿，叶琴，余烨，王宇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海赛可出行科技服务有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">负责任创新；数字创新；TOE框架；共享价值创造</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Responsible innovation, Digital innovation, TOE framework, Shared value creation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近年来，网约车市场迎来爆发式增长，进入百舸争流的“大航海”时代，如何在数字化时代瞬息万变的技术变革与行业竞争下实现负责任的创新成为需要深思的话题。本案例描述了享道出行作为上海汽车集团旗下移动出行战略品牌，坚持合规第一、安全高效、技术赋能，倾力打造高品质服务出行平台的负责任创新实践故事。享道出行自成立之后，将合规性作为企业立身之本，以技术赋能体系化降本增效，在司乘平等、保障品质的前提提升乘客消费的质价比，不断提升服务质量和用户体验，并积极以技术回报社会，全面承担数字企业社会责任，最终跻身行业“独角兽”行列，实现“质与量”“合与创”的健康成长。本案例适用于《创新管理》《商业伦理与企业社会责任》等课程中对“”负责任创新“”相关知识点的学习和研讨。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In recent years, the car-hailing market has ushered in explosive growth and entered the era of &quot;great navigation&quot;. How to achieve responsible innovation in the rapidly changing technological changes and industry competition in the digital era has become a topic that needs to be considered deeply. This case describes the responsible innovation practice of XiangDao Travel, as a strategic mobility brand under Shanghai Automotive Group, which insists on compliance first, safety and efficiency, and technology empowerment, and strives to build a high-quality service mobility platform. Since its establishment, XiangDao Travel has taken compliance as the foundation of the enterprise, used technology to enable systematic cost reduction and efficiency, improved the quality and price ratio of passengers&#39; consumption on the premise of equality and quality assurance, continuously improved service quality and user experience, and actively returned to the society with technology, fully assumed digital corporate social responsibility, and finally joined the ranks of &quot;unicorn&quot; in the industry. This case is suitable for the study and discussion of relevant knowledge points of &quot;Responsible innovation&quot; in courses such as &quot;Innovation Management&quot; and &quot; Business Ethics and Corporate Social Responsibility &quot;.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新管理》、《商业伦理与企业社会责任》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">（1）数字企业负责任创新的内涵与意义；（2）TOE框架下数字企业负责任创新的动因分析；（3）数字企业负责任创新的价值主体与实践内容；（4）基于共享价值创造视角理解数字企业负责任创新的结果</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-02</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9358" target="_blank">点击查看</a></td>
                            </tr>
